text: Hans Sauter (6 June 1925 - 1 October 2014) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed at the 1948, 1952, 1956 and the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bregenz Category:Sportspeople from Vorarlberg
